260
00:17:37,595 --> 00:17:40,133
Eu sou sempre assim, alto e gritando.

261
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:41,409
Você sabe disso.

262
00:17:41,783 --> 00:17:42,614
OK.

263
00:17:42,984 --> 00:17:44,493
